The next important question is: what data to use to inves-
tigate these properties? We use photos of modern sculptures
from Flickr, and describe a procedure for gathering a large
and diverse dataset in Section 4. This data has many de-
sirable properties: it has much greater variety in terms of
shape compared to common-place objects; it is real and in
the wild, so has all the challenging artifacts such as severe
lighting and varying texture that may be missing in syn-
thetic data. Additionally, the dataset is automatically or-
